tories%2F114%2F2012%2F09%2F20120918filmExpendables2.jpg&h=64523bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.巴尼支付了原協議要求的三百萬美元以保障人質安全，但海盜卻坐地起價要求五百萬。岡納則打算直接交火，引致海盜傷亡。岡納隨後因為對被俘的海盜動用私刑，而引發與「陰陽」之間的鬥毆，最後為巴尼所制止，由於岡納太過暴躁，精神極不穩定，巴尼將之驅逐出隊...<br />\n<br />\n2.這支傭兵組成的突擊隊由巴尼（席維斯&middot;史特龍飾）領軍，經過激烈的槍戰，解救了中國富豪和戰壕（阿諾&middot;史瓦辛格飾），最終陰陽（李連杰飾）負責把商人護送回中國，陰陽就此下場。<br />\n回美國後，隊員比利（連恩&middot;漢斯沃飾）說他打算退出，到法國和女朋友團聚。巴尼答應了他的要求。<br />\n接著，巴尼接到了一個中情局情報員「教堂先生」（布魯斯&middot;威利飾）的新任務：去一架墜落在阿爾巴尼亞的中國空軍運輸機上，取回保險箱裏的秘密物品。同時在「教堂先生」的推薦下，華裔女性的陳美琪（余男飾）加入隊伍..<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=bae3397f\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=0cda43c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dc2928e63a5aa77fb13bdab5c5f591c9bce3ed","tid":2289953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f08890630e8cbb11ddca1e60951a10b8a00fba8","tid":2289953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T16:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 